name: Furniture_of_America_Clarks_Farmhouse_Style_Dining_Table
reviews: I bought this without seeing anybody's review. It kind of risky, but it turns out good. color match with description. product was shipped by private freight company. It actually arrived earlier than estimate delivery date. They called you to schedule delivery date and time. Package was well packed with a lot protective materials. Excellent product.
great solid and heavy table, goes well with our old farm house

We are so in love with our farmhouse table ! The color is gorgeous and clean lines give it a more modern look. The finishing is great as well... Glasses left on top have not made permanent rings or anything of the sort. Best furniture buy!
there is patches in the table top and marks in it they look like a hole punchthe top looks tacky but like the color of it and sturdiness
description:
Make your dining area more inviting with this rustic table from Furniture of America. Pair this rectangular oak table with sturdy wood chairs to create a cohesive country-inspired look. This farmhouse-style table is large enough to accommodate up to six seated guests, and the spacious top surface makes it easy to serve a variety of homemade dishes family style.
Set includes: One (1) dining tableMaterials: Solid wood, wood veneerFinish: Dark oakTable dimensions: 30 inches high x 72 inches wide x 40 inches deepStyleCountry, Farmhouse, Rustic, Southwestern, TraditionalMaterialVeneer, WoodFinishBrown Finish, Distressed, Oak Finish, Wood FinishShapeRectangleAssemblyAssembly Required
